race.description: Rmbl Investments Rising Stars Race (Bm62) Handicap
race.comment: TWO SIGMA (9) peaks and has been within range in tougher contests. Cartwright sticks aboard in an apprentices-only race and she maps for a soft run. Well placed to post her second win. BELLALIQUE (2) came from back in the field to just miss at Terang. Has weight relief in this contest and rates to be in the finish. ROSE OF SHALAA (1) has given away big starts her last two but has hit the line in good style. Fourth up now and back a level can't be ruled out if things go her way. LEGACY ROSE (3) dropped back sharply to 1300m at Burrumbeet and just missed. She will be around the mark holding that form.
